trans-unit.source: Base class for types that identify control types, events, patterns, properties, and text attributes in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The AutomationIdentifier class is effectively abstract, as it has no constructor and cannot be instantiated by applications.
